Ok Guys,<br><br>
Worst Meal I ever came upon.  Slopes were out on the perimeter doing their normal useless thing.  They had a little fire going cooking chow.  Had my co-pilot with me just so he could see what was going on.  Boys were roasting a seek and kill dog.  Guess his handler had let him stray too far.  Gooks didn't even skin the critter.  Man burning shepard smells like shit.<br><br>
Well the co was new in country and proceeded to do the puck his guts out trick.  Raving about dog.  Felt better until I told him we had a dog meal the night before down town.  Gee!   Neve knew a guy could puck like that.  Only took 24 hours for for screaming shits to set in.  He never liked my humor<br><br>
He didn't care much for the roasted rice bugs.  AT least they pulled the legs off for him.  (True Story)
